OL,3,CBoy, 15, detained for life for murder
OL,4,Cof Alfie Lewis outside school
OL,6,FA teenager with a "worrying interest
OL,7,Fin knives" has been detained for
OL,8,Fstabbing a 15-year-old boy through the
OL,9,Fheart on his way home from school.
OL,11,FBardia Shojaeifard, 15, has been given
OL,12,Fa life sentence with a minimum term of
OL,13,F13 years for the murder of Alfie
OL,14,FLewis, who was stabbed to death "in
OL,15,Ffull view" of pupils leaving a school
OL,16,Fin Horsforth, Leeds, last November.
OL,18,FShojaeifard, who was 14 at the time,
OL,19,Fwas found guilty of murdering Alfie by
OL,20,Fa Leeds Crown Court jury in April.
