OL,3,CBoy, 15, detained for life for murder
OL,4,Cof Alfie Lewis outside school
OL,6,FAlfie was attacked in a busy street
OL,7,Fduring home time when he was on his
OL,8,Fway to meet friends from Horsforth
OL,9,FSchool, where he had previously been a
OL,10,Fstudent.
OL,12,FShojaeifard had admitted stabbing
OL,13,FAlfie with a 13cm-long kitchen knife
OL,14,Fhe had brought from home but denied
OL,15,Fmurder.
OL,17,FShojaeifard can be named publicly for
OL,18,Fthe first time after the judge, Mr
OL,19,FJustice Cotter, lifted reporting
OL,20,Frestrictions preventing him from being
OL,21,Fidentified on Friday.
