OL,3,CBoy, 15, detained for life for murder
OL,4,Cof Alfie Lewis outside school
OL,6,FHe said lifting the defendant's
OL,7,Fanonymity would help in the "vitally
OL,8,Fimportant debate about the scourge of
OL,9,Fknife crime, among young people in
OL,10,Fparticular".
OL,12,FAlfie's mother, Heather Lane,
OL,13,Faddressed Shojaeifard directly in
OL,14,Fcourt saying she will "never, ever"
OL,15,Fforgive him.
OL,17,FMs Lane sobbed as she said: "Alfie was
OL,18,Fmy heart and when he was stabbed in
OL,19,Fthe heart it killed me too."
