OL,3,CBoy, 15, detained for life for murder
OL,4,Cof Alfie Lewis outside school
OL,6,FShe described Alfie as her "big-
OL,7,Fhearted boy" who was known for
OL,8,F"sorting out everyone's problems and
OL,9,Fbeing the peacekeeper".
OL,11,F"We laughed, danced and smiled, we
OL,12,Floved each other for 15 years and I
OL,13,Fthought we would for the rest of my
OL,14,Flife."
OL,16,FIn a statement read to the court,
OL,17,FAlfie's older brother, Antony Lewis,
OL,18,Fsaid he was his "loving and caring
OL,19,Flittle mate" who "never deserved what
OL,20,Fhappened to him".
