OL,3,CBoy, 15, detained for life for murder
OL,4,Cof Alfie Lewis outside school
OL,6,FThe defendant had claimed he was
OL,7,Fscared of Alfie, but the jury had
OL,8,Fdiscounted his claims and convicted
OL,9,Fhim of murder.
OL,11,FThe judge said he did not accept
OL,12,FShojaeifard's evidence that he was
OL,13,F"trying to scare Alfie away and swung
OL,14,Fthe knife aimlessly".
OL,16,F"You intended to cause him really
OL,17,Fserious harm. You carefully planned to
OL,18,Fconfront Alfie to gain revenge for
OL,19,Fwhatever happened on October 31," the
OL,20,Fjudge told the defendant.
