OL,3,CBoy, 15, detained for life for murder
OL,4,Cof Alfie Lewis outside school
OL,6,FHe said one witness described
OL,7,FShojaeifard's attack as "vicious" and
OL,8,Fthat he was "trying as much as he
OL,9,Fcould to inflict some sort of damage
OL,10,Fto Alfie".
OL,12,FThe judge said: "Alfie was a much
OL,13,Floved and loving son and nephew, a
OL,14,Ffriend to many ` kind and big-hearted
OL,15,Fwith a love of football, something you
OL,16,Fshared, you even played together in
OL,17,FYear 5.
