OL,3,CBoy, 15, detained for life for murder
OL,4,Cof Alfie Lewis outside school
OL,6,F"Despite his difficulties at school he
OL,7,Fhad many positive qualities. He had a
OL,8,Flong life ahead of him and you took
OL,9,Fthat away."
OL,11,FHe added: "Knives have stolen so many
OL,12,Flives, and you and others must
OL,13,Funderstand how dangerous this
OL,14,Fobsession is.
OL,16,F"Without your interest in knives Alfie
OL,17,Fwould be here today."
